================================================================================
PRIVACY COMMITMENT
================================================================================

Luducat:
- Stores all user data locally (XDG standard directories)
- Does NOT transmit personal data to external servers
- Does NOT include analytics or telemetry
- May check luducat.org for updates (version only, configurable)
- Stores credentials in system keyring where available

